00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:23,900
 ali ono, nikako duboko neka vjera,

410
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:26,200
 da budu mama, tata, dobro, baka, di dobro,

411
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:28,720
 da sve nek idem smjerom dobrim

412
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:33,420
 i definitivno se to onda realiziralo u životu,

413
00:25:33,420 --> 00:25:35,100
