00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:12,320
 Ili mislim da...

446
00:27:12,320 --> 00:27:15,440
 Može biti obron, to je povezano,

447
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:17,300
 ali mislim da je originalna u zdravom duhu,

448
00:27:17,300 --> 00:27:17,980
