462
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,580
 A onda te život opet vrati

463
00:27:46,580 --> 00:27:47,340
 i onda opet,

464
00:27:47,340 --> 00:27:48,800
 znam da sam bio u potrazi

465
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:50,640
