 koja meni odgovara

485
00:28:19,120 --> 00:28:20,220
 duše ja radim na večer.

486
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:22,460
 Tako da ti ja,

487
00:28:22,460 --> 00:28:22,840
 eto,

488
00:28:22,840 --> 00:28:24,000
 a opet,

489
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,020
 roditelji

