494
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:32,680
 ko da nisi tu,

495
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,960
 kad ja nešto počnem ovoga,

496
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,100
 svoje,

497
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:37,300
