519
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:05,260
 zdravlja na svim razinama.

520
00:29:05,260 --> 00:29:08,620
 Kako izgleda jedna,

521
00:29:08,620 --> 00:29:10,940
 pretpostavljiv sam kroz ovo,

522
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:11,660
