525
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:21,040
 koju prakticiraš,

526
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:21,980
 recimo svaki dan.

527
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:24,140
 Je li to tako?

528
00:29:24,140 --> 00:29:25,400
 Je, je, da, da.

529
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:28,360
 Kako izgleda jedan tvoj običajni dan?

530
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:30,700
 Moj dan ili tada rutina?

531
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:32,300
 Tvoj dan.

532
00:29:32,300 --> 00:29:32,900
 I recimo,

533
00:29:32,900 --> 00:29:33,800
 kroz, kroz,

534
00:29:33,800 --> 00:29:36,120
