535
00:29:36,120 --> 00:29:38,020
 a koji bi opisao možda

536
00:29:38,020 --> 00:29:39,240
 i taj dio

537
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:41,660
 bavljenja sportom,

538
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:42,860
 prehrane,

539
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:44,280
 pa ono,

540
00:29:44,280 --> 00:29:45,060
