560
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,220
 najlošije cipele.

561
00:30:14,180 --> 00:30:14,580
 E ja,

562
00:30:14,580 --> 00:30:15,260
 Bog me,

563
00:30:15,260 --> 00:30:17,260
 želim da od mene

564
00:30:17,260 --> 00:30:18,440
 budu najbolje cipele.

565
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:20,560
 Tako da ti ja,

566
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:22,700
 mogu ja to i ovako javno reći,

567
00:30:22,700 --> 00:30:23,660
 da je zapravo biohacking,

568
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:25,020
 termin sam kuglao,

569
00:30:25,020 --> 00:30:26,140
 nisam bio ovoga,

570
00:30:26,140 --> 00:30:27,980
 možda sam ga čuvao,

571
00:30:27,980 --> 00:30:29,760
 ali nisam baš ovoga,

572
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:32,100
