603
00:31:07,540 --> 00:31:09,900
 i znam da su prve korekcije

604
00:31:09,900 --> 00:31:10,820
 prehrane bilo,

605
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:12,980
 znači mama kad bi namazala paštetu,

606
00:31:12,980 --> 00:31:13,940
 to bi bilo ono,

607
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:16,860
