608
00:31:16,860 --> 00:31:18,460
 Prvi početci su bili,

609
00:31:18,460 --> 00:31:19,180
 a ne želim,

610
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:22,380
 toliko tanko bi namazao paštetu,

611
00:31:22,380 --> 00:31:24,300
