615
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:32,240
 To su prvi početci neke korekcije,

616
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:34,040
 ne mogu sjeti otkud mi to ono.

617
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:38,060
 A da ti samo kažem,

618
00:31:38,060 --> 00:31:38,800
 i to mogu otkrivit,

619
00:31:38,800 --> 00:31:44,420
 dakle ta moja dizajnirana svakodnevni duhovni skleko,

620
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:45,060
 ja vam to nazvat,

621
00:31:45,060 --> 00:31:45,980
 na večeri radim,

622
00:31:45,980 --> 00:31:48,180
 i to ti se može nazvat,

623
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:48,660
 ajmo reći,

624
00:31:48,660 --> 00:31:52,900
 prvi dio je jedna vrsta molitve,

625
00:31:52,900 --> 00:31:57,740
 srednji dio je jedno nazvat,

626
00:31:57,740 --> 00:31:59,880
 nazovimo to osještavanje,

627
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,160
 svakodnevni,

628
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:05,740
 dakle u danu prođemo onako retrospektivno kroz dan,

629
00:32:05,740 --> 00:32:08,080
 i izražavanje zahvalnosti

630
00:32:08,080 --> 00:32:12,220
 za sve dobro što se dogodilo u danu.

631
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:15,300
 A u danu, kakav god da bio,

632
00:32:15,300 --> 00:32:16,160
