633
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:18,220
 To govorimo da ono,

634
00:32:18,220 --> 00:32:20,720
 da si zahvalan što dišeš,

635
00:32:20,720 --> 00:32:23,960
 ne ono zahvalan što sam ugovorio dobar posao,

636
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:27,000
