637
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:27,980
 zahvalnosti,

638
00:32:27,980 --> 00:32:31,540
 i treći segment

639
00:32:31,540 --> 00:32:33,700
 tih duhovnih sklekova,

640
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:34,940
