1275
00:51:40,560 --> 00:51:43,440
 a ti u tom trenutku misliš o...

1276
00:51:43,440 --> 00:51:46,960
 diš poslije pit kavu, onda je nepravilno, onda nisam to na...

1277
00:51:46,960 --> 00:51:51,600
 I ljudi su to prihvatili i to se radi zadnjih 8 godina svi,

1278
00:51:51,600 --> 00:51:52,840
