1348
00:55:22,860 --> 00:55:24,560
 Sve te svere.

1349
00:55:24,560 --> 00:55:24,960
 Da.

1350
00:55:24,960 --> 00:55:25,800
 Da li si me razumiješ?

1351
00:55:25,800 --> 00:55:26,600
 Razumiješ.

1352
00:55:26,600 --> 00:55:29,720
 Sličan problem imam ja recimo kad jelite svoje healthy fit vikende

1353
00:55:29,720 --> 00:55:31,060
 ili kad nešto u opisu,

