1370
00:56:20,200 --> 00:56:21,920
 prekrasno, izvrsno,

1371
00:56:22,060 --> 00:56:24,940
 za obavit meditaciju ili molitvu,

1372
00:56:24,940 --> 00:56:26,100
 ili šta god.

1373
00:56:26,520 --> 00:56:27,660
 Ali ja kažem ljudi,

1374
00:56:27,660 --> 00:56:29,240
