1447
00:58:56,940 --> 00:58:59,480
 i sad u tom opisu više me muči

1448
00:58:59,480 --> 00:59:01,440
 kada to opišem,

1449
00:59:01,440 --> 00:59:03,300
 nekad znam i preskočiti,

1450
00:59:03,300 --> 00:59:04,520
 ne napisati,

1451
00:59:04,520 --> 00:59:05,420
 a znam da ćemo raditi.

1452
00:59:05,420 --> 00:59:07,260
 Znaš šta, teško je?

1453
00:59:07,260 --> 00:59:09,220
 Jesi, jesi, jesi.

1454
00:59:09,220 --> 00:59:11,560
 Mislim, izuzetno mi je draga ta tematika.

1455
00:59:11,640 --> 00:59:13,280
 Vidim da razmišljaš o tim stvarima isto.

1456
00:59:14,480 --> 00:59:16,100
