1457
00:59:16,100 --> 00:59:17,800
 Znaš, ako imaš,

1458
00:59:17,800 --> 00:59:19,600
 ja ovako se izrazim,

1459
00:59:19,600 --> 00:59:22,480
 avatar, avatar su neke različite skupine ljudi,

1460
00:59:22,480 --> 00:59:23,380
 recimo, rekli si,

1461
00:59:23,380 --> 00:59:25,140
 neki su možda kršćani, katolici,

1462
00:59:25,140 --> 00:59:28,960
 neki su totalno suprotno od toga,

1463
00:59:28,960 --> 00:59:30,980
 neki su u tom mindfulness-u,

1464
00:59:30,980 --> 00:59:32,820
 neki su u ezoteriji,

1465
00:59:32,820 --> 00:59:33,320
 neki su...

